{"tid":469381,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"用moving average去做forecasting其實有咩好處?","createTime":"2017-11-15T09:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T12:31:48.000Z","uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1eae7518e1af000f28a476077bd90678e2ae7386","tid":469381,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"Moving average有細分做:<br />\n1) Simple moving average<br />\n2) Weighted moving average<br />\n3) Exponential moving average<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moving_average#Weighted_moving_average\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMoving_average%23Weighted_moving_average&d=ywWURTQq08Fzn72WMUz%2Fuf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4a6f7c9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moving_average#Weighted_moving_average</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綜合咁睇 Moving average用黎做forecasting有咩好處?同埋處理有邊啲特性嘅數據比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而3種分開講 邊隻幾時啱用? 純粹比較recent data比起old data重要幾多去決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81129cd9f086fbc2c8a1fb11c5ecdc99cff0938","tid":469381,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Moving average有細分做:<br />\n1) Simple moving average<br />\n2) Weighted moving average<br />\n3) Exponential moving average<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moving_average#Weighted_moving_average\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMoving_average%23Weighted_moving_average&d=ywWURTQq08Fzn72WMUz%2Fuf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4a6f7c9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moving_average#Weighted_moving_average</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綜合咁睇 Moving average用黎做forecasting有咩好處?同埋處理有邊啲特性嘅數據比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而3種分開講 邊隻幾時啱用? 純粹比較recent data比起old data重要幾多去決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似會冇咁受 outliers 影響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文科人路過出返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd7386c2952476f7fe60b3d7d7563b6ad1d9587","tid":469381,"uid":50428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:23:29.000Z","msg":"&quot;純粹比較recent data比起old data重要幾多去決定&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係, 佢地既分別就係近既Ratio大d, 咁既話個意義就會係想強調愈近愈重要。 一係就係depends on 邊一個最Fit 個實際情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處應該係識跟住d data 郁, 一paste 新data落excel 就做晒, 我自己就predict stock price 用過。 其實都係 time series <br />\n<br />\n等睇其他高見學野。"},{"pid":"ed900b0ada540094a61079e9493d7b5cd3431d83","tid":469381,"uid":50428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:35:32.000Z","msg":"同埋因為都係為左睇邊個準/FIT番原本個情況, 通常都係一野做晒 處理晒D raw data 最後砌好多條model先check  d model 邊條先似,所以或者個好處係比多個樣去形容你D data 應該係點走"},{"pid":"fa2d32aac6c302bf10dbf5695e38fc73c2b74bf5","tid":469381,"uid":37489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:02:55.000Z","msg":"減少high frequency perturbations"},{"pid":"2748245f0dcf95ed02ba37252f42b16c3f5e2865","tid":469381,"uid":147022,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"成班讀書讀壞腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b26c4efb44fba7ca63144a08687d59ff45f3f7","tid":469381,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&quot;純粹比較recent data比起old data重要幾多去決定&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係, 佢地既分別就係近既Ratio大d, 咁既話個意義就會係想強調愈近愈重要。 一係就係depends on 邊一個最Fit 個實際情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處應該係識跟住d data 郁, 一paste 新data落excel 就做晒, 我自己就predict stock price 用過。 其實都係 time series <br />\n<br />\n等睇其他高見學野。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Thanks"},{"pid":"9828e1e61b70a567ec881e6b48aeaa33361e0098","tid":469381,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班讀書讀壞腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"}]}